title: Then Came Bronson
description:
A fair copy of the &#039;Then Came Bronson&#039; movie (series pilot), made in 1969.  Taped from TV, edited out commercials and then put on DVD.  If you are a collector this is not for you.  If you want to watch the movie, this may be the right one.

NTSC-English only.

This is a re-upload of the original that was at: http://thepiratebay.se/tor/3431514/Then_Came_Bronson.  I deleted the original torrent file so I can&#039;t re-seed (or figure out how to).  Smooth huh?

I&#039;m going to super-seed this for a few days only on request and then it&#039;s up to you guys to keep it going.
